They've all hit memorable shots at the climax to the Race to Dubai, but could any of them match - or even better - each other in a unique challenge on the Earth Course?

That was the task for Rory McIlroy, Justin Rose and Henrik Stenson earlier this week when the trio warmed-up for the DP World Tour Championship by trying to recreate each other's famous shots on the 18th hole at the tournament.

Stenson's effort - a stunning three wood approach to the green which won the European Tour's Shot of the Year award in 2013 - was first up for McIlroy and Rose.

